e2fsprogs are the standard userspace programs for ext2, ext3, and ext4 filesystems.

== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=sys-fs/e2fsprogs|desc=Optional USE flags for {{Package|sys-fs/e2fsprogs}} include:
|nls+yes+yes
|static-libs
}}

=== Emerge ===

The {{Package|sys-fs/e2fsprogs}} package and should be available as part of the default system profile.

{{Emerge|sys-fs/e2fsprogs}}

== Configuration ==

=== Files ===

Global configuration files:

* {{Path|/etc/e2fsck.conf}}
* {{Path|/etc/mke2fs.conf}}

